-lrb- the hollywood reporter -rrb- good news arrived thursday for `` fifty shades of grey '' fans .
universal announced thursday that the sequel to the box office blockbuster will hit theaters on feb. 10 , 2017 .
the third film in the series will debut feb. 9 , 2018 .
the news came one day after the hollywood reporter reported exclusively that the husband of el james , author of the `` fifty shades '' trilogy , will write the script for the second film .